quran[10]{c,v,t}:
  45,23,"“Kodi wamuona amene wachichita chilakolako chake kukhala mulungu wake wompembedza? Ndipo Allah wamlekelera kuti asokere, kupyolera mkudziwa Kwake; ndipo wamdinda (chidindo) mmakutu mwake ndi mu mtima mwake ndi kumuika chivindikiro mmaso mwake. Choncho ndani angamuongole pambuyo pa Allah? Kodi simukumbukira"
  45,24,"“Ndipo (okanira kuuka ku imfa) adanena: “Kulibe (moyo wina) koma moyo wathu womwewu wa padziko lapansi; timafa ndi kukhala ndi moyo; palibe chikutiononga koma nthawi basi.” Koma iwo alibe kudziwa pa zimene akunenazo; akungoganizira chabe"
  45,25,"“Ndipo Ayah Zathu zikawerengcdwa kwa iwo zolongosola chilichonse momveka, alibe mtsutso wina koma kunena kuti: “Tibweretsereni makolo Athu (aukitseni akhale ndi moyo) ngati inu muli owona!”"
  45,26,"“Nena (kwa iwo iwe Mtumiki): “Allah amakupatsani moyo. Kenako amakupatsani imfa. Kenako adzakusonkhanitsani tsiku la Qiyâma lopanda chikaiko.” Koma anthu ambiri sakudziwa"
  45,27,"“Ndipo ufumu wa kumwamba ndi pansi ngwa Allah, ndipo tsiku limene Qiyâma idzachitika, (anthu) ogwirizana ndi zonama adzaonongeka patsikulo"
  45,28,"“Ndipo udzaliona gulu lililonse litagwada (uku nkhope zili zyoli); gulu lililonse lidzaitanidwa ku kaundula wake (kukamuwerenga): “Lero mulipidwa zimene mudali kuchita!”"
  45,29,““Uyu kaundula Wathu akunena zoona za inu; ndithu Ife tidali kulemba zimene mudali kuchita.”
  45,30,"“Koma amene adakhulupirira ndi kuchita zabwino, Mbuye wawo adzawalowetsa ku chifundo Chake; kumeneko ndiko kupambana koonekera"
  45,31,"“Ndipo amene adakanira, (adzauzidwa kuti): “Kodi Ayah Zanga sizidali kuwerengedwa kwa inu? Koma inu mudadzikweza; ndipo mudali anthu oipa.”"
  45,32,"“Ndipo kukanenedwa kuti lonjezo la Allah ndiloona, ndikuti Qiyâma ilibe chikaiko, mudali kunena: “Sitikudziwa Qiyâma kuti nchiyani; tikungoganizira chabe, ndipo tilibe chitsimikizo (cha Kiyamayo).”"